2. The Super Admin Panel (Body Corporate)
â€¢ Unit & Role Creation: The ability to create the 26 units (14 businesses, 12 residential) and assign a "Group Admin" login to each.
â€¢ Site Capacity Tracker: A visual warning system monitoring how many of the Impro SLP935 software's "Sites" have been used, preventing the system from hitting hard limits.
